generalProductInformationModule.name: Depend Fitted Maxiumn Protection Briefs S/M, 20ct, 4pk

components.longDescription:
• Medium size fits individuals with waist sizes 19" to 34", hip sizes 26" to 41" and weight under 170 Ibs
  • Ultra ABSORB-LOCProtection quickly absorbs and locks fluids away
  • Stay-Dry liner keeps moisture away from skin
  • Soft leakage barriers guard against side leakage for comfortable protection
  • 6 EasyGrip tabs are easier to grasp and refasten
  • Gentle elastic leg gathers help provide a comfortable fit for better protection
  • More underwear-like color
  • Wetness indicators
  • Elastic waist allows brief to be pulled up and down with a snug fit
  • Unisex
